# General
CONFIG_VERBOSE (prints a lot of debug information to the screen)
CONFIG_TTY_VGA (choose VGA driver, 80x20 resolution)
CONFIG_TTY_VBE (use the VESA BIOS Extension, 1920x1080 resolution)
CONFIG_RTC (enables the RTC with datetime support)

# Virtual Memory Manager
CONFIG_UVMM_FIRSTFIT
CONFIG_UVMM_BESTFIT
CONFIG_UVMM_WORSTFIT
CONFIG_UVMM_NEXTFIT
CONFIG_READ_AFTER_FREE_PROT (after each free the memory is zeroed)

# Scheduler
CONFIG_ROUND_ROBIN (round-robin scheduling algorithm)
CONFIG_FCFS_SCH (simple scheduling alg. - executing a task until finished)
CONFIG_RR_TIME_QUANTUM (time quantum for the round-robin scheduler)

# Shell
CONFIG_HOSTNAME (change hostname)
CONFIG_BACKGROUND_COLOR (change background color)
CONFIG_TEXT_COLOR (change text color)
CONFIG_SH_HISTORY (enable shell command history)

